批俾火燒死"},{"pid":"6549153afecbe86d3d1e4f44c8e89814fbe9218d","tid":551870,"uid":12633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T06:12:32.000Z","msg":"連 natural law 都唔識，好心唔好登呢條垃圾既言論啦。<br />\n<br />\np.s. Natural Law 由 Thomas Hobbes 所提倡，及後被君主所採用，以法律取代教會地位，從此各國開始以法律治國、而非以宗教治國。"},{"pid":"bb0d1d99318d3a4690a3e1579ab93a42442b1372","tid":551870,"uid":62409,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T06:13:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.wonkette.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/jesus-finger-500.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.wonkette.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2014%2F12%2Fjesus-finger-500.jpg&h=243ff3f1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4765db17e3464327854182ea9ee8092197cb12c7","tid":551870,"uid":21772,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6549153afecbe86d3d1e4f44c8e89814fbe9218d","tid":551870,"uid":12633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T06:12:32.000Z","msg":"連 natural law 都唔識，好心唔好登呢條垃圾既言論啦。<br />\n<br />\np.s. Natural Law 由 Thomas Hobbes 所提倡，及後被君主所採用，以法律取代教會地位，從此各國開始以法律治國、而非以宗教治國。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T06:56:03.000Z","msg":"份報紙佢架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad70386a10053b3253121eaffb8832295a60faf4","tid":551870,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T06:57:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nOn撚咗9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}